accessibility.text: CDC recs for adults:  Prevnar f/b Pneumovac (better memory)
Diagnostic for SAD: Pneumovax (titers before/after), wait 6 months, check memory, give Prevnar if needed
CDC recs for adults:  Prevnar f/b Pneumovac (better memory)
Diagnostic for SAD: Pneumovax (titers before/after), wait 6 months, check memory, give Prevnar if needed
Look for >1.3 or 2-4 fold increase titer, ideally 50-75% of strains improve
